| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5089 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 69d9548f-1cbe-54b4-ae10-326c69e1a23a"
